title: Game4Ukraine was about much more than football as Arsenal star hails 'powerful message sent to world'
description: The line-up had been billed as a Panini sticker album brought to life… so many football legends on a pitch at the same time.

title: Mother of Scout says son faced 'hugely uncomfortable' conditions during blistering heatwave
description: The "concerned" mother of a teenager evacuated from the World Scout Jamboree during a heatwave in South Korea says her son faced "hugely uncomfortable" conditions at the event.

title: Imran Khan accused Pakistan government of 'dismantling democracy' before arrest
description: Pakistan's former prime minister Imran Khan said his party had faced unprecedented "victimisation" and accused the country's government of "dismantling democracy" in an an interview before his latest arrest.

title: Russian soprano who refused to condemn Putin sues US opera house after she was dropped
description: A Russian singer, who was dropped by a US opera house because she refused to renounce Vladimir Putin's war in Ukraine, is suing her former employer.

title: Widespread protests possible as Khan arrest adds tension to Pakistan's febrile political climate
description: Imran Khan has always said the mounting cases against him are politically motivated and intended to stop him from running for election.

title: Another Russian tanker hit by sea drone near Crimean Bridge, Moscow says
description: A Russian-flagged tanker close to the Crimean Bridge has been hit by a Ukrainian sea drone, Moscow has said.

title: Former Pakistan PM Imran Khan arrested over corruption charges
description: Imran Khan, Pakistan's former prime minister, has been arrested over corruption charges, his lawyer has said.

title: 'Because of Interpol my life is destroyed': Bahrain accused of abusing the red notice system
description: Campaigners say Bahrain is abusing the Interpol red notice system to track down and extradite dissidents from abroad.

title: Abandoned walrus pup given constant cuddles to try and keep him alive
description: An abandoned walrus pup is receiving round-the-clock "cuddling" from welfare workers trying to keep him alive.

title: 'Ambulances everywhere' - UK Scout leader reveals Jamboree chaos amid South Korea heatwave
description: A UK Scout leader at the World Jamboree in South Korea has described conditions as "atrocious and unusable".
